{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775845273928,"sessionID":"ses_2876256cbffe4Ah7wokpE7l1AJ","part":{"id":"prt_d78a070e90010Hv8U43IivWWHz","messageID":"msg_d789e72a6001QAZ9KpBBmMx8WJ","sessionID":"ses_2876256cbffe4Ah7wokpE7l1AJ","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-b9b028d93c6442bcbce80fb535b47f9d","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-006/tasks.md","content":"# AR-006 — Sandbox 删除与生命周期管理 Tasks\n\n## Metadata\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-006 — Sandbox 删除与生命周期管理 |\n| Module | `pkg/workloadmanager` |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | M |\n| Design | [Stage ST-3 completed] |\n\n---\n\n## Task Checklist\n\n### Phase 1: Store Interface Extensions\n\n- [ ] **T1.1** Add `ListExpiredSandboxes` method to Store interface in `pkg/workloadmanager/types.go`\n  - Signature: `ListExpiredSandboxes(ctx context.Context, before time.Time, limit int) ([]*types.SandboxInfo, error)`\n  - Verify: `grep -q \"ListExpiredSandboxes\" pkg/workloadmanager/types.go`\n\n- [ ] **T1.2** Add `ListInactiveSandboxes` method to Store interface in `pkg/workloadmanager/types.go`\n  - Signature: `ListInactiveSandboxes(ctx context.Context, before time.Time, limit int) ([]*types.SandboxInfo, error)`\n  - Verify: `grep -q \"ListInactiveSandboxes\" pkg/workloadmanager/types.go`\n\n- [ ] **T1.3** Create mock Store implementation for testing in `pkg/workloadmanager/mock_store.go`\n  - Implement all Store interface methods with map-backed storage\n  - Implement ListExpiredSandboxes filtering by ExpiresAt < before, limit results\n  - Implement ListInactiveSandboxes filtering by LastActivity < before, limit results\n  - Verify: `go build ./pkg/workloadmanager/...`\n\n- [ ] **T1.4** Create tests for mock Store in `pkg/workloadmanager/mock_store_test.go`\n  - Test ListExpiredSandboxes returns expired sandboxes only\n  - Test ListInactiveSandboxes returns inactive sandboxes only\n  - Test limit parameter respects batch size\n  - Verify: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/... -run TestMockStore -v`\n\n### Phase 2: LifecycleConfig & Types\n\n- [ ] **T2.1** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/lifecycle.go` - LifecycleConfig struct\n  - Define LifecycleConfig struct with fields:\n    - `DefaultTTL time.Duration` (default: 8h)\n    - `DefaultIdleTimeout time.Duration` (default: 15m)\n    - `DefaultMaxDuration time.Duration` (default: 8h)\n    - `GCInterval time.Duration` (default: 2min)\n    - `GCOnceTimeout time.Duration` (default: 2min)\n    - `DeletionGracePeriod int64` (default: 0)\n    - `DeletionTimeout time.Duration` (default: 30s)\n  - Verify: `grep -q \"type LifecycleConfig struct\" pkg/workloadmanager/lifecycle.go`\n\n- [ ] **T2.2** Create `DefaultLifecycleConfig()` function in `pkg/workloadmanager/lifecycle.go`\n  - Return LifecycleConfig with values from defaults.go constants\n  - Verify: `grep -q \"func DefaultLifecycleConfig\" pkg/workloadmanager/lifecycle.go`\n\n- [ ] **T2.3** Create tests for LifecycleConfig in `pkg/workloadmanager/lifecycle_test.go`\n  - Test DefaultLifecycleConfig returns correct values\n  - Verify: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/... -run TestLifecycleConfig -v`\n\n### Phase 3: SandboxLifecycleManager Core\n\n- [ ] **T3.1** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/lifecycle.go` - SandboxLifecycleManager struct\n  - Define SandboxLifecycleManager struct with fields:\n    - `k8sClient *K8sClient`\n    - `store Store`\n    - `config LifecycleConfig`\n    - `logger Logger`\n  - Verify: `grep -q \"type SandboxLifecycleManager struct\" pkg/workloadmanager/lifecycle.go`\n\n- [ ] **T3.2** Create `NewSandboxLifecycleManager` constructor in `pkg/workloadmanager/lifecycle.go`\n  - Signature: `NewSandboxLifecycleManager(k8sClient *K8sClient, store Store, config LifecycleConfig, logger Logger) *SandboxLifecycleManager`\n  - Verify: `grep -q \"func NewSandboxLifecycleManager\" pkg/workloadmanager/lifecycle.go`\n\n- [ ] **T3.3** Implement `DeleteSandbox` method in `pkg/workloadmanager/lifecycle.go`\n  - Steps:\n    1. Get sandbox info from store (return NotFoundError if not found)\n    2. Delete Sandbox CR via dynamic client using SandboxGVR\n    3. Delete SandboxClaim if Kind == \"SandboxClaim\"\n    4. Delete from store\n  - Use metav1.DeleteOptions with DeletionGracePeriod\n  - Handle apierrors.IsNotFound as success (already deleted)\n  - Verify: `grep -q \"func.*DeleteSandbox\" pkg/workloadmanager/lifecycle.go`\n\n- [ ] **T3.4** Implement `IsExpired` method in `pkg/workloadmanager/lifecycle.go`\n  - Signature: `IsExpired(sandbox *types.SandboxInfo) bool`\n  - Return `time.Now().After(sandbox.ExpiresAt)`\n  - Verify: `grep -q \"func.*IsExpired\" pkg/workloadmanager/lifecycle.go`\n\n- [ ] **T3.5** Implement `IsIdleExpired` method in `pkg/workloadmanager/lifecycle.go`\n  - Signature: `IsIdleExpired(sandbox *types.SandboxInfo, idleTimeout time.Duration) bool`\n  - Return false if LastActivity.IsZero()\n  - Return `time.Now().After(sandbox.LastActivity.Add(idleTimeout))`\n  - Verify: `grep -q \"func.*IsIdleExpired\" pkg/workloadmanager/lifecycle.go`\n\n- [ ] **T3.6** Implement `ForceDeleteSandbox` method in `pkg/workloadmanager/lifecycle.go`\n  - Use GracePeriodSeconds=0 for immediate deletion\n  - Delete from store regardless of CR deletion result\n  - Verify: `grep -q \"func.*ForceDeleteSandbox\" pkg/workloadmanager/lifecycle.go`\n\n- [ ] **T3.7** Create tests for DeleteSandbox in `pkg/workloadmanager/lifecycle_test.go`\n  - Test successful deletion flow\n  - Test NotFound error handling (IsNotFound treated as success)\n  - Test K8s API error handling\n  - Test store deletion after CR deletion\n  - Verify: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/... -run TestDeleteSandbox -v`\n\n- [ ] **T3.8** Create tests for IsExpired and IsIdleExpired in `pkg/workloadmanager/lifecycle_test.go`\n  - Test IsExpired with expired sandbox\n  - Test IsExpired with non-expired sandbox\n  - Test IsIdleExpired with zero LastActivity\n  - Te